    <entry>
      <title>算法竞赛技巧积累</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/18/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E7%A7%AF%E7%B4%AF/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/18/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E7%A7%AF%E7%B4%AF/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><h1 id="0x01-基础知识"><a href="#0x01-基础知识" class="headerlink" title="0x01 基础知识"></a>0x01 基础知识</h1><ul><li>尽量缩短变量的定义范围。例如，在<code>for</code>循环的初始化部分定义循环变量。</li><li>不拘一格地使用伪代码来思考和描述算法。</li><li>C99中只规定了int类型至少是16位，却没有规定具体值，但规定了一些固定长度的整数，例如<code>int32_t</code>、<code>uint32_t</code>。在当前流行的竞赛平台中，int 都是32位整数，范围是<code>-2147483648 ~  2147483647</code>。</li><li>在循环体开始处定义的变量，每次执行循环体的时会重新声明并初始化。</li><li>在多数据的题目中，一个常见的错误：在计算完一组数据后某些变量没有重置，影响到下组数据的求解。</li></ul><h1 id="0x02-取整"><a href="#0x02-取整" class="headerlink" title="0x02 取整"></a>0x02 取整</h1><h2 id="01-floor"><a href="#01-floor" class="headerlink" title="01. floor()"></a>01. floor()</h2><ul><li><p><strong>语法</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;math.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">double</span> <span class="title">floor</span><span class="params">( <span class="keyword">double</span> arg )</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>功能</strong>：向下取整，函数返回不大于<em>arg</em>的最大整数值。</p></li><li><p><strong>实例</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">floor</span>(+<span class="number">2.7</span>) = +<span class="number">2.0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">floor</span>(<span class="number">-2.7</span>) = <span class="number">-3.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="02-ceil"><a href="#02-ceil" class="headerlink" title="02. ceil()"></a>02. ceil()</h2><ul><li><p><strong>语法</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;math.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">double</span> <span class="title">ceil</span><span class="params">( <span class="keyword">double</span> arg )</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>功能</strong>：向上取整，函数返回不小于<em>arg</em>的最大整数值。</p></li><li><p><strong>实例</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ceil</span>(+<span class="number">2.7</span>) = +<span class="number">3.0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ceil</span>(<span class="number">-2.7</span>) = <span class="number">-2.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="03-四舍五入"><a href="#03-四舍五入" class="headerlink" title="03. 四舍五入"></a>03. 四舍五入</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> tar = <span class="built_in">floor</span>(sou + <span class="number">0.5</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="0x03-输入输出"><a href="#0x03-输入输出" class="headerlink" title="0x03 输入输出"></a>0x03 输入输出</h1><h2 id="01-普通文件操作"><a href="#01-普通文件操作" class="headerlink" title="01. 普通文件操作"></a>01. 普通文件操作</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">FILE *fin, *fout;</span><br><span class="line">fin = fopen(<span class="string">"data.in"</span>, <span class="string">"rb"</span>);<span class="comment">//读打开</span></span><br><span class="line">fout = fopen(<span class="string">"data.out"</span>, <span class="string">"wb"</span>);<span class="comment">//写打开</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">fscanf</span>(fin, <span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;x);<span class="comment">//读</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout, <span class="string">"%d"</span>, x);<span class="comment">//写</span></span><br><span class="line">fclose(fin);<span class="comment">//关闭文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="02-重定向"><a href="#02-重定向" class="headerlink" title="02. 重定向"></a>02. 重定向</h2><p>重定向后就与标准输入输出效果一样了，所有读键盘输入、写键盘输出的函数都将改用文件。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">freopen(<span class="string">"data.in"</span>, <span class="string">"r"</span>, <span class="built_in">stdin</span>);<span class="comment">//读打开</span></span><br><span class="line">freopen(<span class="string">"data.out"</span>, <span class="string">"w"</span>, <span class="built_in">stdout</span>);<span class="comment">//写打开</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="03-鲁棒性"><a href="#03-鲁棒性" class="headerlink" title="03. 鲁棒性"></a>03. 鲁棒性</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;n) == <span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>n=0</code>为输入标记，但还要判断scanf的返回值，为了鲁棒性。算法竞赛中题目的输入输出是人设计的，难免会出错，有时会出现题目指明以<code>n=0</code>为结束标志而真实数据忘记以<code>n=0</code>结尾的情形。</p>]]></content>
      
      
